plotdata <- Marriage %>%

  count(race) %>%
  arrange(desc(race)) %>%
  mutate(prop = round(n * 100 / sum(n), 1),
         lab.ypos = cumsum(prop) - 0.5 *prop)

  ggplot(plotdata,
  aes(x = "",
      y = prop,
      fill = race))+
    geom_bar(width = 1,
             stat = "identity",
             color = "black") +
    coord_polar("y",
                start = 0,
                direction = -1) +
    theme_void()

  summarize(mean_salary = mean(salary))

       aes(x = rank,
           y = mean_salary)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity")
